    {
      "type": "LinguisticObject",
      "content": "The live creation act carried out by Sun & Rain Works during Sotheby's Photographs auction on March 30, 2009. The primary work is the auction itself, designated as artwork (The Auction as Artwork); within that gesture Sun & Rain Works also produced two artifact-parts in real time: the born-digital website www.wtfisart.com and the auction performance work WTF is Ansel Adams. This record gathers the shared creation time and context so the parts reference one documented act rather than duplicating it.",
